		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I will see what I can contribute then.
<br />
<br />I would like to add some extra section to the programming one once I find the information.  When you start to program on a new platform, you always want to know which tools you can use to achieve certain goals like, for example in the case of the nes:
<br />
<br />- list of available assembler/compiler
<br />- graphic editor for tile
<br />- map editor
<br />- music editor
<br />and more
<br />
<br />Then, once I understand more the platform, if time allows me, I want to contribute some section about the common pitfalls I had when I started to program.  I'm sure most beginner ends up with the same common problems. A list of those problems with solution could be beneficial to any aspiring new nes developer.
<br />
<br />And maybe, instead of adding extra comment to the reference, if they are comments from a programmer's perspective, they should be added as explanation to the reference in the programmer's section.

		

